Test 1: Normal input
Input:
  favourite_food = "pizza"
  favourite_place = "goa"
Expected:
  Program prints all personal info, favourite_food, favourite_place, and age in months. No error messages.

Test 2: Empty food once
Input:
  favourite_food = ""  (press Enter)
  favourite_food = "burger"
  favourite_place = "delhi"
Expected:
  Shows "enter your favourite food (cannot be empty)" once.
  Asks again and then prints final information correctly.

Test 3: Long strings
Input:
  favourite_food = "veryverylongfoodname"
  favourite_place = "averyverylongplacename"
Expected:
  Program still prints full lines without crashing or cutting text.
